libfacts (2.0.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Safe execution: fork/exec wrapper with crash detection, timeout, niceness.
  * Runtime test registration via --facts_find (dlsym-based).
  * --facts_register_all to print FACTS_REGISTER_ALL block.
  * Removed auto-discovery (memory scanning). Explicit registration required.
  * New CLI options: --facts_unsafe, --facts_timeout=N.

 -- Warren MacEvoy <wmacevoy@gmail.com>  Thu, 05 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
